00038},{"text":"To claim the title.","quest_name":"Flames of Heart","quest_id":121000038},{"text":"Was that not your unfulfilled wish?","quest_name":"Flames of Heart","quest_id":121000038},{"text":"But I do. Without a champion and the Lion Beast, I cannot touch the Central Hub left by Imperator.","quest_name":"Flames of Heart","quest_id":121000038},{"text":"You... Cartethyia, both my \"daughters,\" my very creations! Why this fruitless resistance?","quest_name":"Flames of Heart","quest_id":121000038},{"text":"Has Septimont ever granted you kindness?","quest_name":"Flames of Heart","quest_id":121000038},{"text":"They neither love you nor need you. Long have you been forgotten.","quest_name":"Flames of Heart","quest_id":121000038},{"text":"Proud in battle, and yet yearning for strength. I know the heart of the Septimontians far better than you.","quest_name":"Flames of Heart","quest_id":121000038},{"text":"Mya, you are simply too afraid to face their true nature. You choose to deceive yourself.","quest_name":"Flames of Heart","quest_id":121000038},{"text":"You cannot admit that they used you and then cast you aside. You cannot accept that, from the start, you were insignificant.","quest_name":"Flames of Heart","quest_id":121000038},{"text":"Hush. It matters not. Your thoughts are of little consequence.","quest_name":"Flames of Heart","quest_id":121000038}]}